      "span_text": "Similarly, an algorithm for digital image forgery detection based on shadow detection of the spliced object was presented in  by Tuba et al. They based their algorithm on the fact that a shadow wouldn't change the surface texture, thus if two adjacent areas (with and without shadow) had different texture, then the image could very likely be forged.",
